WEBVTT

00:06.424 --> 00:09.427
(BAGPIPER PLAYS
'AMAZING GRACE')

00:14.849 --> 00:16.351
(EXOTIC DRUMMING)

00:16.518 --> 00:20.855
SHELLEY: <i>We held the service
at sunset just as you requested.</i>

00:21.022 --> 00:23.566
<i>It was syncretic,</i>

00:23.733 --> 00:26.611
<i>combining
the best of everything,</i>

00:26.778 --> 00:29.698
<i>just like you, Uncle Johann.</i>

00:30.782 --> 00:33.743
<i>I loved the monks
and the bells.</i>

00:33.910 --> 00:37.956
<i>I've never seen so many
lotus blossoms in one place.</i>

00:38.123 --> 00:40.125
<i>It was beautiful.</i>

00:41.126 --> 00:43.086
<i>One of these days,
I'd like to arrange</i>

00:43.253 --> 00:47.465
<i>a ceremony like yours
for Uncle Norman too.</i>

00:47.632 --> 00:51.511
<i>I know you and he didn't
always see eye to eye,</i>

00:51.678 --> 00:54.681
<i>but you were both
like fathers to me.</i>

00:55.682 --> 01:00.270
<i>Maybe you can be friends
in heaven, if that exists.</i>

01:01.896 --> 01:04.107
<i>I love you, dear Uncle Johann,</i>

01:04.274 --> 01:07.736
<i>for showing me
what love looks like.</i>

01:08.737 --> 01:13.783
<i>Now I see it at work
in the world...everywhere.</i>

01:14.784 --> 01:17.454
<i>I already miss you so much.</i>

01:18.538 --> 01:22.459
<i>I know that you uploaded
your consciousness into the cloud</i>

01:22.625 --> 01:25.712
<i>and this email's
going up there too.</i>

01:26.713 --> 01:29.966
<i>So maybe my cloud
will touch your cloud one day</i>

01:30.133 --> 01:31.926
<i>and you'll read this.</i>

01:33.052 --> 01:35.597
<i>Goodbye, Uncle Johann.</i>

